  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>

        <div xml:id="Kali90-kilavi">
          <p type="edition">itu “pullutaṉ mayakkum pulavik kaṇṇum” (to.po.151) eṉpataṉāṟ ṟalaivaṉ pulappaṭap 
            parattaiyariṭattu oḻukātu maṟaintoḻuki vantu niṉṟavaṉuṭaṉ kāmakkiḻatti ūṭic collit talaimakaṉ 
            āṟṟāmai kaṇṭu taṉ āṟṟāmaiyuñ colli ūṭaṟīrntatu.</p>
          <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"></p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="Kali90">
            <lg type="edition">
                <l>kaṇṭēṉiṉ māyaṅ kaḷavātal poynnakā</l>
                <l>maṇṭāta collit toṭāa ṟoṭīiyaniṉ</l>
                <l>peṇṭi ruḷarmaṉṉō vīṅku;</l>
                <l rend="space">oṇṭoṭinī, kaṇṭa tevaṉō tavaṟu;</l>
                <l rend="space">kaṇṭatu, nōyum vaṭuvuṅ karantu makiḻcerukkip</l>
                <l>pāṭu peyaṉiṉṟa pāṉā ḷiraviṟ</l>
                <l>ṟoṭipoli tōḷu mulaiyuṅ katuppum</l>
                <l>vaṭivār kuḻaiyu miḻaiyum poṟaiyā</l>
                <l>voṭivatu pōlu nucuppō ṭaṭitaḷarā</l>
                <l>vārāk kavavi ṉoruttivan talkaṟṟaṉ</l>
                <l>cīrār ñekiḻañ cilampac civantuniṉ</l>
                <l>pōrār katava mititta tamaiyumō</l>
                <l>vāyiḻai yārkku molikēḷā vavvetir</l>
                <l>tāḻā teḻuntunī ceṉṟa tamaiyumō</l>
                <l>māṟāḷ ciṉaiiyava ḷāṅkēniṉ mārpi</l>
                <l>ṉāṟiṇarp paintār parinta tamaiyumō</l>
                <l>tēṟinī tīyē ṉalēṉeṉṟu maṟṟavaḷ</l>
                <l>cīṟaṭi tōyā viṟutta tamaiyumō</l>
                <l>kūṟiṉik kāyēmō yām;</l>
                <l rend="space">tēṟiṟ, piṟavun tavaṟilēṉ yāṉ;</l>
                <l rend="space">alkaṟ, kaṉavuko ṉīkaṇ ṭatu;</l>
                <l rend="space">kaṉaipeyaṟ ṟaṇṭuḷi vīcum poḻutiṟ kuṟivantāṭ</l> <!-- removed comma after kaṉaipeyaṟ because it was upsetting sandhi -->
                <l>kaṇṭa kaṉaveṉak kāṇātu māṟuṟṟup</l>
                <l>paṇṭaiya vallaniṉ poyccū ṇiṉakkellā</l>
                <l>niṉṟāyniṉ pukkil pala;</l>
                <l rend="space">meṉṟōḷāy, nalkuniṉ ṉalleḻi luṇku;</l>
                <l rend="space">ēṭā, kuṟaiyuṟṟu nīyem muraiyaṉiṉ ṟīmai</l>
                <l>poṟaiyāṟṟē meṉṟal peṟutumō yāḻa</l>
                <l>niṟaiyāṟṟā neñcuṭai yēm.</l>
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                <l></l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
